@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h2 class="mb-3">Privacy Policy</h2>
    <hr />

    <p class="text-muted">
        This system is used internally by TechMove GLMS to manage clients, contracts, and service requests.
        All information processed through this platform is handled responsibly and securely.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">Data Usage</h4>
    <p>
        The data captured in this system is used solely for operational, administrative, and service‑delivery purposes.
        No personal or business information is sold, shared, or distributed to external parties.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">Data Security</h4>
    <p>
        TechMove GLMS follows secure handling practices to protect sensitive information, including contract documents,
        client details, and service request records. Access to this system is restricted to authorized personnel only.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">Document Storage</h4>
    <p>
        Uploaded documents, such as signed agreements, are stored securely and are only accessible to authorized users
        for operational purposes.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">User Responsibility</h4>
    <p>
        Users accessing this system are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of their login credentials
        and ensuring that data is used only for legitimate business functions.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">Contact</h4>
    <p>
        For questions regarding data handling or privacy practices, please contact the system administrator.
    </p>
</div>
